reviews.content: I always thought these beer gardens were successful based on selling cheap food and a lot of beer to groups of men.  This place surprised me.  It was clean and well decorated.  I brought the entire family and we discovered the food was …

I just had a chance to visit the restaurant and was really impressed! The space is spacious, airy, and it's extremely comfortable to sit and drink with friends. The food comes out quickly, is hot, and is very tasty, especially the salads, …
The food comes out quickly and the staff is enthusiastic. But there are too many smokers.
Spacious street front location, convenient for parking and moving. Good food, ok price, a bit crowded.

. The restaurant cooks quite delicious food. Reasonable price . When it first opened, the wait for food took a long time, probably because the restaurant was too crowded. The next few times I came back, the restaurant was …
Spacious and airy restaurant Like it because the food is delicious and fast
Affordable prices. Delicious food. The staff are also quite enthusiastic. Dishes are served much faster than when they first opened. I will support this restaurant for a long time.
Saw a crowd near my house so I stopped by to eat. The food was okay but it took too long to order.

The food is delicious and tasty. If you come on the weekend, you should book a table in advance, otherwise when you come, you have to wait for a table, sometimes there is no table to sit, because the restaurant is crowded.

The restaurant is beautiful, clean, delicious food, airy space. There are quite a lot of customers so the food doesn't come out very quickly, but it's understandable because there are too many customers. The food is delicious so it's worth the wait.
